ly closes Strait of Hormuz\n• Commercial vessels hit by missiles\n• Trump at NATO: \"Ceasefire is over\"\n\nThe MOU is dead. WTI back at $71. Here's where oil stands.\n\nPrevious: https://t.co/sdt280IzVl\n#OOTT #WTI #Oil", "time": "07:47", "author": "NexQuantRes", "author_name": "Next Quantitative Research", "followers": 45, "views": 528, "likes": 1, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Iran", "Prices/technicals", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2076215407350882597", "url": "https://x.com/DB_WTI/status/2076215407350882597", "text": "#OOTT #WTI \n#US strikes #Iran, #Tehran hits #Gulf states, says Strait of #Hormuz closed https://t.co/nuqPaCsW5M", "time": "08:01", "author": "DB_WTI", "author_name": "WTI Trading Group- 🇺🇸 US Crude Oil Trader🛢️🌎", "followers": 12440, "views": 1409, "likes": 0, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2076218524700188892", "url": "https://x.com/NexQuantRes/status/2076218524700188892", "text": "Gold $4,114. Silver $60.17.\n\nHormuz is closed. Iran is firing on tankers. Russia is at war.\n\nYet gold is $1,500 below its January high and stuck in a range.\n\nBecause geopolitics doesn't drive gold. Rates do. A fact-based thread. \n#OOTT #Gold #Silver", "time": "08:14", "author": "NexQuantRes", "author_name": "Next Quantitative Research", "followers": 45, "views": 438, "likes": 3, "replies": 2, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2076235044524290102", "url": "https://x.com/albertrjf/status/2076235044524290102", "text": "This was before the announcement from today, so it should come down even more! Really not near enough to b